Output demo.gif

Set Shell zsh
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 900
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 20ms

Type "cli-speedrun"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Enter
Sleep 500ms

Enter
Sleep 4s

Type "git add ."
Sleep 500ms
Type "git commit -m 'init'"
Sleep 500ms
Type "git push origin main"
Sleep 500ms

Escape
Sleep 500ms
Type "q"
Sleep 500ms
